{"id":"56bdf762-2dab-40a8-8c53-3554d114ca25","name":"Medkit","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em>“Let’s not do that again.”</em></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/CBIxawn1qG9fqwbzP8pSt.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 79, 66);\">⫘⫘⫘</span><span style=\"color: rgb(38, 131, 106);\">⫘⫘⫘</span><span style=\"color: rgb(71, 244, 198);\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</span><span style=\"color: rgb(57, 175, 143);\">⫘⫘⫘</span><span style=\"color: rgb(49, 166, 135);\">⫘</span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 99, 82);\">⫘⫘⫘</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\">“Do you ever get the feeling that something is wrong? Like a constant itch in the back of your head? Like you’re standing in the wrong place at the wrong time, except the feeling never goes away…?</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(46, 255, 235);\">I wake up like that. Every day.</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\">I don’t remember the last time I woke up and didn’t immediately check the room… Not that it matters. Sleep isn’t… useful anyway, it’s just a different place for things to haunt me.</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\">When I spawned with a Support Gear they said I was <em>lucky</em>, you know:</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(46, 255, 235);\"> “Rare spawn”, “Valuable asset”, “Remarkable capabilities.”</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\">Those words stopped sounding like compliments the moment I realized they weren’t about <em>me</em>, but what I can do…</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(177, 255, 229);\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(46, 255, 235);\"><strong>Healing</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(177, 255, 229);\"><strong>.</strong>&nbsp;No one ever cared about</span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\"> what it does to me to know that the only reason anyone keeps me around is because I can put them back together after they get hurt.</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\">I worked with someone named </span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 111, 209);\"><strong>Sub</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 139, 228);\"><strong>spa</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(255, 195, 236);\"><strong>ce</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\">… well, “Worked together” is generous. We tolerated each other, barely. He had this particular way of speaking as if everything and everyone was already beneath him… I didn’t like him.</span></p><p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; color: rgb(4, 0, 71);\"><em>.</em></span></p><p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px; color: rgb(186, 255, 248);\">But as long as the results of our crystal r","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"3bQnEhVs6xT63WAmlGldT.webp","creator":"Haunter!","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","🦄 Non-human","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":852,"messages":36172,"created_at":"2025-12-08T16:43:59.089845+00:00"}